WEBVTT

00:00:00.040 --> 00:00:14.740
( Watch on Kissasia.vip )

00:00:43.760 --> 00:00:44.360
No.

00:00:44.600 --> 00:00:45.640
Who are you, miss?

00:00:45.920 --> 00:00:46.520
Miss,

00:00:46.800 --> 00:00:48.000
do we know each other?

00:00:48.240 --> 00:00:48.680
Young Master,

00:00:48.680 --> 00:00:50.140
I've been waiting for you.

00:01:00.440 --> 00:01:01.760
Why are you touching me?

00:01:01.760 --> 00:01:03.090
Let go before you speak.

00:01:05.239 --> 00:01:06.320
I'm sorry, sir.

00:01:06.680 --> 00:01:08.410
I mistook you for someone else.

00:01:08.800 --> 00:01:09.320
Sir,

00:01:09.320 --> 00:01:11.039
you can't enter the Lin Residence without an invitation now.

00:01:11.039 --> 00:01:13.120
Not everyone in this town is a local.

00:01:13.760 --> 00:01:14.720
Be careful.

00:01:17.039 --> 00:01:18.039
What she just said,

00:01:18.039 --> 00:01:19.770
is it the taboo of Luoxian Town?

00:01:20.000 --> 00:01:20.560
Lin Mo,

00:01:20.560 --> 00:01:21.560
are you okay?

00:01:22.560 --> 00:01:23.200
I'm fine.

00:01:24.039 --> 00:01:25.570
This place is very strange.

00:01:26.240 --> 00:01:28.120
Let's go find the male lead first.

00:01:30.560 --> 00:01:32.120
Try the tracking talisman to see if it works.

00:01:32.120 --> 00:01:32.920
Find someone

00:01:32.920 --> 00:01:33.979
named Han Qingyun,

00:01:34.200 --> 00:01:35.840
under twenty years old.

00:01:38.600 --> 00:01:40.460
Talismans cannot be used either.

00:01:41.560 --> 00:01:42.960
Let's ask the local village head.

00:01:42.960 --> 00:01:43.490
Let's go.

00:01:48.840 --> 00:01:49.400
Sirs,

00:01:49.400 --> 00:01:50.330
enjoy your meal.

00:01:53.759 --> 00:01:54.880
Miss Chu,

00:01:55.479 --> 00:01:57.759
is your intelligence wrong?

00:01:57.759 --> 00:02:00.160
This town looks quite peaceful.

00:02:00.360 --> 00:02:01.280
It's not what you called

00:02:01.280 --> 00:02:02.940
a place swarming with demons.

00:02:03.520 --> 00:02:04.680
Exactly, sis.

00:02:04.960 --> 00:02:06.820
Look at these vibrant mountains.

00:02:07.120 --> 00:02:08.560
The people here are so simple and honest.

00:02:08.560 --> 00:02:09.759
How could it be a demonic stronghold?

00:02:09.759 --> 00:02:11.320
The Records of a Hundred Demons in my father's archives

00:02:11.320 --> 00:02:12.240
clearly record that

00:02:12.240 --> 00:02:14.040
the sealed land must be swarming with demons.

00:02:14.040 --> 00:02:15.440
It can't be wrong.

00:02:16.600 --> 00:02:18.040
It's normal during the day.

00:02:18.040 --> 00:02:20.170
Did you send anyone to patrol at night?

00:02:21.360 --> 00:02:23.720
I sent people to scout around the town at night.

00:02:23.720 --> 00:02:25.400
Except for the night watchmen, brides,

00:02:25.400 --> 00:02:26.560
and funerals,

00:02:26.920 --> 00:02:28.450
there was nothing unusual.

00:02:29.000 --> 00:02:29.640
Wait.

00:02:30.040 --> 00:02:32.240
Getting married and holding funerals at midnight,

00:02:32.240 --> 00:02:33.160
is that normal?

00:02:33.280 --> 00:02:34.960
That's just the local custom.

00:02:34.960 --> 00:02:37.000
I've strolled around Luoxian Town 800 times early in the morning.

00:02:37.000 --> 00:02:38.720
I didn't sense any demonic aura.

00:02:38.720 --> 00:02:40.480
You can sense demonic aura?

00:02:40.480 --> 00:02:42.680
Aren't you just highwaymen,

00:02:42.760 --> 00:02:44.240
greenwood heroes?

00:02:44.600 --> 00:02:46.640
You are underestimating us.

00:02:46.640 --> 00:02:49.240
My second brother used to be a demon hunter too.

00:02:50.040 --> 00:02:53.240
It's just that he didn't make it into the Tianji Pavilion.

00:02:53.560 --> 00:02:54.800
A rogue cultivator.

00:02:56.000 --> 00:02:58.160
Anyway, regardless of whether this place is suspicious or not,

00:02:58.160 --> 00:02:59.320
I will still pay you.

00:02:59.760 --> 00:03:01.160
After we evacuate from here,

00:03:01.160 --> 00:03:02.760
I will settle the final payment.

00:03:02.760 --> 00:03:03.520
Alright.

00:03:03.520 --> 00:03:04.680
The nobles of Beijing

00:03:04.680 --> 00:03:05.920
are so generous.

00:03:06.040 --> 00:03:06.800
Rest assured,

00:03:06.800 --> 00:03:09.200
we will protect you with our lives.

00:03:09.280 --> 00:03:10.440
Right, Second Boss?

00:03:11.720 --> 00:03:12.650
Second Brother.

00:03:12.840 --> 00:03:13.770
Second Brother.

00:03:28.200 --> 00:03:29.200
Young Master Lin,

00:03:29.400 --> 00:03:30.640
these are Luoxian Town's

00:03:30.640 --> 00:03:32.160
local chronicles for the past five years.

00:03:32.160 --> 00:03:33.220
Please take a look.

00:03:35.040 --> 00:03:36.040
Thank you, Mayor.

00:03:36.920 --> 00:03:37.640
Mayor,

00:03:37.960 --> 00:03:38.880
do you know

00:03:38.880 --> 00:03:41.079
of a young man in town named Han Qingyun?

00:03:41.640 --> 00:03:42.280
Yes.

00:03:42.360 --> 00:03:44.160
He is the town's herb gatherer.

00:03:44.280 --> 00:03:45.680
He went up the mountain to gather herbs today.

00:03:45.680 --> 00:03:46.810
When will he be back?

00:03:46.920 --> 00:03:49.120
A trip takes about ten days.

00:03:49.680 --> 00:03:51.240
Did something happen?

00:03:52.200 --> 00:03:53.640
We are also investigating.

00:03:53.640 --> 00:03:55.200
Do you know of anything unusual

00:03:55.200 --> 00:03:56.520
happening in town recently?

00:03:56.520 --> 00:03:57.760
Anything unusual?

00:03:58.200 --> 00:03:58.920
No.

00:03:59.920 --> 00:04:01.160
Mr. Lin,

00:04:01.160 --> 00:04:03.040
please have some tea first.

00:04:03.240 --> 00:04:04.040
Here.

00:04:05.440 --> 00:04:06.240
Have some tea.

00:04:07.280 --> 00:04:08.080
Thank you.

00:04:08.800 --> 00:04:10.640
Are there any missing persons here

00:04:10.640 --> 00:04:12.170
who haven't been found yet?

00:04:12.920 --> 00:04:14.380
Why do you call him Mr. Lin?

00:04:14.560 --> 00:04:16.120
Calling him so affectionately.

00:04:16.120 --> 00:04:16.839
Young Master Lin

00:04:16.839 --> 00:04:18.970
is a great philanthropist in our town.

00:04:19.600 --> 00:04:22.240
Luoxian Town owes its current prosperity

00:04:22.360 --> 00:04:23.840
entirely to the salt industry developed by Young Master Lin.

00:04:23.840 --> 00:04:24.720
Yes.

00:04:25.400 --> 00:04:27.730
Young Master Lin has been kind to all of us.

00:04:28.440 --> 00:04:29.040
Mayor,

00:04:29.160 --> 00:04:30.000
to be honest,

00:04:30.360 --> 00:04:31.600
I had a little accident

00:04:31.600 --> 00:04:33.000
and forgot a lot of things.

00:04:33.000 --> 00:04:33.840
Do you know

00:04:33.840 --> 00:04:36.840
why I was arrested by the Huaiyang County government?

00:04:37.200 --> 00:04:37.560
You,

00:04:37.560 --> 00:04:39.520
you were arrested by the government?

00:04:39.520 --> 00:04:40.720
When did this happen?

00:04:40.880 --> 00:04:42.640
I only know that you had a falling out with your family

00:04:42.640 --> 00:04:43.840
and left Luoxian Town overnight.

00:04:43.840 --> 00:04:44.520
Since then,

00:04:44.520 --> 00:04:46.440
the Lin Manor also carried out a major purge.

00:04:46.440 --> 00:04:47.560
Then do you know

00:04:47.880 --> 00:04:48.960
what Lin Mo's current relationship

00:04:48.960 --> 00:04:50.360
with the Lin family is?

00:04:50.520 --> 00:04:52.320
After Young Master Lin was kicked out of the Lin Manor,

00:04:52.320 --> 00:04:54.159
the Lin Manor kept its doors tightly closed

00:04:54.159 --> 00:04:55.800
and no longer received guests.

00:04:55.800 --> 00:04:56.880
Yes.

00:04:57.360 --> 00:04:59.520
No one ever went into the manor again,

00:04:59.960 --> 00:05:01.720
and no one ever came out.

00:05:02.080 --> 00:05:02.800
Then

00:05:02.800 --> 00:05:04.840
is there any way to get into the Lin Manor?

00:05:04.840 --> 00:05:05.880
No.

00:05:06.400 --> 00:05:08.200
No one can enter.

00:05:09.840 --> 00:05:10.360
Madam.

00:05:10.600 --> 00:05:11.530
Go get some rest.

00:05:11.680 --> 00:05:12.800
I'm here.

00:05:14.920 --> 00:05:15.280
Mayor!

00:05:15.280 --> 00:05:15.840
Stop right there.

00:05:15.840 --> 00:05:17.040
Mayor, save me!

00:05:17.640 --> 00:05:19.000
I'll go out and take a look.

00:05:19.000 --> 00:05:19.080
- Mayor! -

00:05:19.080 --> 00:05:19.760
Mayor!

00:05:21.560 --> 00:05:22.200
Mayor!

00:05:22.720 --> 00:05:23.920
Isn't this Shopkeeper Wu?

00:05:23.920 --> 00:05:25.600
Let's talk this over.

00:05:25.600 --> 00:05:26.760
This is none of your business.

00:05:26.760 --> 00:05:28.160
Go home and hug your wife.

00:05:28.360 --> 00:05:29.680
It's no use running to the mayor's house.

00:05:29.680 --> 00:05:30.000
Come with me.

00:05:30.000 --> 00:05:30.520
No matter what,

00:05:30.520 --> 00:05:31.800
you can't just snatch a girl

00:05:31.800 --> 00:05:33.200
in broad daylight.

00:05:33.280 --> 00:05:35.000
Her brother owes me money and can't pay it back.

00:05:35.000 --> 00:05:36.000
Using his sister to pay off the debt

00:05:36.000 --> 00:05:37.400
is perfectly justified.

00:05:37.640 --> 00:05:38.240
Mayor!

00:05:39.920 --> 00:05:40.440
Mayor!

00:05:40.640 --> 00:05:41.320
You signed it,

00:05:41.320 --> 00:05:41.840
you have to accept it.

00:05:41.840 --> 00:05:42.440
No!

00:05:42.720 --> 00:05:44.159
Mayor, save me!

00:05:45.520 --> 00:05:45.880
Brother!

00:05:45.880 --> 00:05:46.640
I said,

00:05:46.840 --> 00:05:48.640
I'll pay back the money I owe you.

00:05:48.720 --> 00:05:50.120
If you dare to target my sister again,

00:05:50.120 --> 00:05:51.850
I'll risk my life fighting you.

00:05:57.200 --> 00:05:57.840
What are you looking at?

00:05:57.840 --> 00:05:58.520
Get him!

00:06:06.960 --> 00:06:07.360
I,

00:06:07.360 --> 00:06:08.240
I have an IOU.

00:06:08.440 --> 00:06:10.100
His sister signed it herself.

00:06:10.320 --> 00:06:11.120
If they can't pay back the goods,

00:06:11.120 --> 00:06:13.250
she'll use herself to pay off the debt.

00:06:15.040 --> 00:06:15.970
Where is the IOU?

00:06:16.720 --> 00:06:17.600
Let us see it.

00:06:18.040 --> 00:06:19.160
Stealthy Substitution,

00:06:19.160 --> 00:06:19.920
activate!

00:06:22.520 --> 00:06:23.440
Young Boss.

00:06:24.640 --> 00:06:25.440
This...

00:06:27.800 --> 00:06:28.600
Miss Chu.

00:06:29.200 --> 00:06:30.960
We're wandering the streets like this.

00:06:30.960 --> 00:06:32.440
What exactly are you looking for?

00:06:32.440 --> 00:06:33.360
Looking for a pattern.

00:06:33.360 --> 00:06:34.240
What pattern?

00:06:34.320 --> 00:06:36.380
Some kind of pattern in Luoxian Town.

00:06:37.520 --> 00:06:38.640
Working at sunrise,

00:06:38.640 --> 00:06:39.900
and resting at sunset.

00:06:40.840 --> 00:06:42.159
That's a normal pattern.

00:06:42.159 --> 00:06:43.440
I'm looking for abnormal ones.

00:06:43.440 --> 00:06:44.760
Like what you said,

00:06:44.760 --> 00:06:46.520
weddings and funerals happening at night.

00:06:46.520 --> 00:06:48.800
Then we should wait until night to stake out.

00:06:48.800 --> 00:06:50.440
The sun hasn't even set yet.

00:06:50.640 --> 00:06:51.920
You're obviously an amateur.

00:06:51.920 --> 00:06:54.450
Daytime anomalies are the key breakthrough.

00:06:55.120 --> 00:06:55.560
Fine.

00:06:55.560 --> 00:06:56.840
Anyway, as long as I follow you around,

00:06:56.840 --> 00:06:57.760
I get paid.

00:06:57.760 --> 00:06:59.000
This is not a bad deal.

00:07:00.120 --> 00:07:01.400
I'll just follow you.

00:07:01.840 --> 00:07:02.960
No IOU,

00:07:02.960 --> 00:07:04.040
baseless slander,

00:07:04.120 --> 00:07:06.380
and kidnapping a girl in broad daylight.

00:07:06.960 --> 00:07:08.720
This voice sounds familiar.

00:07:09.240 --> 00:07:09.800
My lord.

00:07:09.800 --> 00:07:11.040
Help me. It was just in my clothes.

00:07:11.040 --> 00:07:12.000
Where did it go?

00:07:12.440 --> 00:07:13.400
A dispute.

00:07:13.440 --> 00:07:14.240
A good sign.

00:07:14.440 --> 00:07:15.200
Let's go take a look.

00:07:15.200 --> 00:07:15.960
Let's go.

00:07:17.240 --> 00:07:18.520
Without evidence,

00:07:18.720 --> 00:07:19.960
if you dare to grab someone again,

00:07:19.960 --> 00:07:21.520
it will be kidnapping.

00:07:22.040 --> 00:07:23.640
I'll settle the score with you two later.

00:07:23.640 --> 00:07:24.440
Young Master,

00:07:24.560 --> 00:07:25.920
why bother coming back?

00:07:26.280 --> 00:07:27.940
Isn't it better to stay alive?

00:07:29.120 --> 00:07:29.760
Let's go.

00:07:31.720 --> 00:07:32.440
Wait.

00:07:32.640 --> 00:07:33.970
Don't you recognize me?

00:07:36.760 --> 00:07:37.920
I am Han Qingyun.

00:07:40.520 --> 00:07:42.320
This is my sister, Han Xiaoying.

00:07:42.480 --> 00:07:43.920
Thank you all for saving us.

00:07:43.920 --> 00:07:44.800
Thank you all.

00:07:44.840 --> 00:07:46.120
Thank you, brothers.

00:07:47.040 --> 00:07:48.040
Mayor,

00:07:48.440 --> 00:07:51.500
didn't you say he went to the mountains to gather herbs?

00:07:52.880 --> 00:07:54.240
Why did you deceive us?

00:07:56.280 --> 00:07:57.120
Yeah.

00:07:57.800 --> 00:07:58.720
Why did you lie?

00:07:59.320 --> 00:08:02.040
I was afraid you would make things difficult for this child.

00:08:02.040 --> 00:08:04.080
Why would he rather be in debt

00:08:04.080 --> 00:08:05.440
than go into the mountains to gather herbs?

00:08:05.440 --> 00:08:06.720
The mountains...

00:08:06.720 --> 00:08:08.980
The mountains haven't been safe lately.

00:08:13.280 --> 00:08:14.320
Little brother,

00:08:14.680 --> 00:08:16.540
you're hiding something from us.

00:08:24.080 --> 00:08:24.800
Master.

00:08:25.920 --> 00:08:28.180
There are marks of a coffin on the ground.

00:08:28.720 --> 00:08:29.240
Mayor,

00:08:29.840 --> 00:08:31.900
did you have a funeral in your family?

00:08:33.080 --> 00:08:35.280
There was a coffin parked at your door.

00:08:36.000 --> 00:08:36.929
Who passed away?

00:08:37.640 --> 00:08:38.799
How is that possible?

00:08:38.799 --> 00:08:40.720
No one in my family died.

00:08:41.039 --> 00:08:42.840
My wife and I don't even have children.

00:08:42.840 --> 00:08:44.039
The whole town knows about it.

00:08:44.039 --> 00:08:47.170
It's a huge taboo to drop a coffin at someone's doorstep.

00:08:47.560 --> 00:08:49.440
If it wasn't your family's funeral,

00:08:49.440 --> 00:08:50.440
then whose was it?

00:08:51.240 --> 00:08:52.080
Village Head,

00:08:52.440 --> 00:08:53.760
are you hiding something from us?

00:08:53.760 --> 00:08:54.560
What?

00:08:54.760 --> 00:08:56.560
What could I possibly be hiding?

00:08:57.400 --> 00:08:57.800
Yes.

00:08:57.800 --> 00:09:00.440
Maybe the coffin bearers just came over to rest their feet.

00:09:00.440 --> 00:09:01.120
This...

00:09:01.360 --> 00:09:02.760
With so many people in town,

00:09:02.760 --> 00:09:04.020
isn't it normal to have

00:09:04.160 --> 00:09:05.160
weddings and funerals?

00:09:05.160 --> 00:09:05.760
Right?

00:09:05.800 --> 00:09:07.480
What could I be hiding?

00:09:07.920 --> 00:09:08.960
Nothing?

00:09:10.960 --> 00:09:14.440
Then why does your town have a custom of holding funerals at night?

00:09:14.440 --> 00:09:17.100
Looks like we ran into someone in the same trade.

00:09:17.280 --> 00:09:18.520
It's you.

00:09:19.240 --> 00:09:21.170
I knew you were no ordinary person.

00:09:21.400 --> 00:09:22.400
I trust you've been well,

00:09:22.400 --> 00:09:23.360
Mr. Lin.

00:09:23.360 --> 00:09:24.360
Where's my stuff?

00:09:24.400 --> 00:09:25.060
What stuff?

00:09:25.160 --> 00:09:26.760
I have no idea what you're talking about.

00:09:26.760 --> 00:09:27.600
Lin Mo.

00:09:27.920 --> 00:09:29.200
Who is she?

00:09:31.720 --> 00:09:32.440
An inmate.

00:09:33.160 --> 00:09:35.360
You never give anyone a moment's peace.

00:09:35.480 --> 00:09:37.040
I barely know her.

00:09:38.440 --> 00:09:40.240
I'll deal with you later.

00:09:41.000 --> 00:09:41.640
Mayor.

00:09:41.640 --> 00:09:42.840
I'm not that easygoing.

00:09:42.840 --> 00:09:43.480
Tell me,

00:09:43.640 --> 00:09:45.640
why are all the weddings and funerals in Luoxian Town

00:09:45.640 --> 00:09:47.370
held in the middle of the night?

00:09:48.400 --> 00:09:49.040
Mayor.

00:09:49.520 --> 00:09:50.720
Isn't this unusual?

00:09:52.840 --> 00:09:54.300
The sun is almost setting.

00:09:55.240 --> 00:09:57.440
You should hurry and find a place to stay.

00:09:57.440 --> 00:09:59.700
Whatever you do, don't come out at night.

00:09:59.960 --> 00:10:01.290
Still not talking, huh?

00:10:01.560 --> 00:10:02.600
Li Dashan.

00:10:02.600 --> 00:10:03.600
Break one of his legs.

00:10:03.600 --> 00:10:04.440
Okay.

00:10:07.480 --> 00:10:08.600
What are you doing?

00:10:08.760 --> 00:10:10.090
Mind your own business.

00:10:10.520 --> 00:10:11.320
Wait.

00:10:12.440 --> 00:10:13.040
Mayor.

00:10:13.520 --> 00:10:14.850
What exactly happened?

00:10:15.040 --> 00:10:16.040
Tell us the truth.

00:10:16.920 --> 00:10:17.760
Have a clear conscience.

00:10:17.760 --> 00:10:18.440
Start.

00:10:20.640 --> 00:10:21.520
Mr. Lin!

00:10:23.480 --> 00:10:24.340
I remember now!

00:10:25.200 --> 00:10:26.320
I remember now!

00:10:26.560 --> 00:10:27.360
Mr. Lin!

00:10:29.760 --> 00:10:32.520
Someone died in my house.

00:10:32.560 --> 00:10:34.800
It was my wife.

00:10:36.120 --> 00:10:38.980
They came at night with a coffin to collect the body.

00:10:39.080 --> 00:10:41.920
That coffin took my wife away.

00:10:41.920 --> 00:10:42.840
Mr. Lin.

00:10:43.480 --> 00:10:44.720
Mr. Lin.

00:10:44.720 --> 00:10:45.560
Mayor.

00:10:45.560 --> 00:10:46.720
What are you talking about?

00:10:46.720 --> 00:10:48.520
Isn't your wife in the house?

00:10:48.520 --> 00:10:49.400
She...

00:10:49.640 --> 00:10:50.960
She is not my wife.

00:10:51.240 --> 00:10:51.920
She is wearing

00:10:51.920 --> 00:10:53.600
my wife's skin.

00:11:02.720 --> 00:11:04.000
Why?

